  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>When you pull up the hood of this nondescript gray cloak (an Interact action), you become drab and uninteresting, gaining a +2 item bonus to Stealth checks and to Deception checks to @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.AJstokjdG6iDjVjE]{Impersonate} a forgettable background character, such as a servant, but also taking a -1 item penalty to Diplomacy and Intimidation checks.</p>\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-effects.Item.uXEp1rPU5fY4OiBf]{Effect: Clandestine Cloak (Greater)}</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Activate</strong> <span class=\"action-glyph\">D</span> envision, Interact</p>\n<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per day</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> You pull the cloak's hood up and gain the benefits of a 5th-level <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.EoKBlgf6Smt8opaU]{Veil of Privacy}</em> for 8 hours or until you pull the hood back down, whichever comes first.</p>"
